    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cred_body",
      "x": 915,
      "y": 588,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "provider auth - two modes, per-env config:\noauth (Claude sub) | api-key (Anthropic key)\none Firestore credentials singleton (encrypted)\nproactive refresh -> retry-once on 401 -> alert\n(s7: terminal failures typed CredentialError ->\ngateway 503 credential_error, never a masked 502;\n/health claudeAuth.lastProviderError = class+ts only)",
      "originalText": "provider auth - two modes, per-env config:\noauth (Claude sub) | api-key (Anthropic key)\none Firestore credentials singleton (encrypted)\nproactive refresh -> retry-once on 401 -> alert\n(s7: terminal failures typed CredentialError ->\ngateway 503 credential_error, never a masked 502;\n/health claudeAuth.lastProviderError = class+ts only)",
