      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "rawText": "S3 count_tokens 2026-07-17: POST /v1/messages/count_tokens (+ /messages alias) forwards through the\nchokepoint - full anonymisation posture, S2 tier resolution (honest counts), 401 refresh-retry - but\nNEVER billed, NEVER rate-capped, allowance-exempt (free upstream; Claude Code polls it continuously).\nBody-limit fix: the global 1 MB parser skips /api/v1/llm, the gateway's own 50 MB parser is live, and\ngateway parse errors answer in the Anthropic error shape (413/400 invalid_request_error).",
      "updated": 1784279797426
